Class Effect ¶

Synopsis

Attributes
duration

number How long the effect will last in seconds
level

integer How strong the effect will be: ex Strenght II
id

integer The numerical identifier of the effect
effectTimeText

string The formated text of the time remaining (ex: 6:45)
name

string The name of the effect ex: night_vision
vname

string The visual name ex: Night Vision II
